The new screen displays various apps related to AliExpress, with the top result being "AliExpress Exclusive Deals" by AI Shopping Assistant. This change indicates that the search query has been processed and the app store has returned relevant applications.
response: The screen will navigate to the AliExpress website or app, displaying its homepage or search results related to "aliexpress."

action: Tap on the "Stopwatch" tab in the top navigation bar to switch to the stopwatch view.
changes: The screen transitions from the Alarm tab to the Stopwatch tab. The main display changes from showing alarm times to showing a large circular timer with the elapsed time "1:91". The navigation bar highlights the "Stopwatch" tab, and the bottom of the screen shows "Reset" and "Share" buttons with a play button in the center.

action: Swipe up from the middle of the screen to scroll down and reveal more options on the product page.
changes: After the swipe action, the "Add to cart" button becomes visible below the "Buy It Now" button, which was previously out of view. The rest of the page content remains unchanged, including the product details, price, and seller information. The bottom app promotion bar is still present.
response:
After swiping up from the middle of the screen, the product page will scroll down to reveal additional information or options that are currently hidden below the visible area. This may include:

- More detailed product specifications or descriptions.
- Customer reviews or ratings.
- Related products or accessories.
- Shipping and return policy details.
- Seller information or contact options.
- Additional purchase options (e.g., financing, gift options).

The ‚ÄúBuy It Now‚Äù button and current visible elements will move upward, and new content will appear at the bottom of the screen, enhancing the user‚Äôs understanding of the product and purchase options.
